Title: Valid username

Feature: As a user, I want to be able to login with the correct username to my account, so that I will be able to gain access. 

Acceptance criteria
If I enter correct values for username (and password) the login should pass. 


Scenario: Test login with correct username

Given: I am on chrome browser and navigate to the login page "https://login.dev.qa-experience.com"
When: I enter Username as "test@qa-experience.com"
And:  I enter password as "Password1"
Then: Login should pass
